Package: cuems-dmxplayer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         librtmidi6,
         libola1
Description: DMX player for Linux with MTC sync and OSC support
 dmxplayer is a Linux-based DMX cue player that uses OLA (Open Lighting
 Architecture), RtMidi, and OSC libraries to play DMX cues with MTC
 (MIDI Time Code) synchronization. It also receives OSC commands to
 configure settings dynamically.
 .
 This package provides the main dmxplayer binary.

